title: Citizen Eco-Drive Silhouette Crystal Silver Tone Womens Watch FE1150-58H - Overview
description:
Citizen Eco-Drive Silhouette Crystal Silver Tone Womens Watch - FE1150-58H http://www.abt.com/product/92562/Citizen-FE115058H.html

Freshen up your watch collection this season ladies with the new Citizen Silhouette Crystal. Fashion forward and ready to be shown off with a unique decorated dial with Swarovski crystals. Shown here in a stainless steel case and bracelet with grey dial featuring date.

• Functions: 3-Hand with Date
• Band: Silver-Tone Stainless Steel Bracelet Fold Over Clasp with Push Button
• Case Size:b 29mm
• Case Material: Silver-Tone Stainless Steel Swarovski Crystal Bezel
• Dial: Spherical Crystal
• Crystal Mineral: Spherical Crystal
• Water-Resistance: 30M
